{
  "stem": "17626.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it wasn't an easy thing because there were barricades.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Streets were crowded with dead horses and wagons overturned and cars and people, mostly people-- dead people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father and my uncle got back to our house before, and since they didn't see Mother, the two of them ventured out into the streets turning over every dead woman and child to see if it was my mother and I.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sure it must have been great joy for them to encounter one another again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After that, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we had no home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what span of time, you know, whether it was the same day, whether it was a few days later, whether they were able to collect some of their belongings if anything was left.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But what I do remember is that we went outside of Warsaw to a village called [POLISH] near the Russian border, where my mother and I used to vacation summertimes and where her family lived.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She had cousins and they lived there all year round.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we used to come there to refresh in the summertime.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we went there-- this was still, from what we understood, standing still and was not bombed as yet.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who knew what was going on?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't imagine my mom and dad even suspected what would happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Mom-- grandmother, rather-- didn't want to go and neither did my Uncle Saul.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the two of them stayed in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my father and mother and I, we went on to the family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PUASES] We were there [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] quite a few months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not quite sure what length of time, during which time my mother was deathly ill.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was hospitalized.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was very ill.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
